---

## Analytical Approach
- Bottom-up cost modelling
- Clear separation of fixed vs variable costs
- Revenue modelling aligned with customer behaviour
- Conservative assumptions suitable for early-stage feasibility analysis

---

## Tools Used
- Microsoft Excel (financial modelling)
- Scenario-based planning
- Unit economics analysis
- Fintech product pricing logic

---

## Limitations & Next Steps
This model represents an **initial feasibility analysis** and does not include:
- Regulatory capital requirements
- Detailed risk-weighted cost structures
- Marketing funnel optimisation
- Investor-grade valuation outputs

Future iterations could incorporate:
- Advanced scenario analysis
- Stress testing
- Multi-year forecasting
- Sensitivity analysis on pricing and churn

---

## Confidentiality Note
This repository contains a **sanitised and high-level version** of the financial model.

Certain assumptions, figures, and internal references have been modified or excluded to respect confidentiality.

